"Managing general agent" does not include:
an employee of the insurer;
a United States manager of the United States branch of an alien insurer;
an attorney in fact authorized by and acting for the subscribers of a reciprocal insurer under a power of attorney;
an authorized insurance producer acting for a surety insurer that engages exclusively in the business of issuing bail bonds; or
